recital.p:
Following an application from VAB-nutrition, submitted pursuant to Article 14(1)(b) of Regulation (EC) No 1924/2006, the Authority was required to deliver an opinion on a health claim related to vitamin D and contribution to the normal function of the immune system (Question No EFSA-Q-2014-00826


                        EFSA Journal 2015;13(5):4096.
                  ). The claim proposed by the applicant was worded as follows: 'Vitamin D contributes to the normal function of the immune system'.
